    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Magpie's Swag (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 5 Gnosis.</em> A spiritually expanded container.</p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> This container holds up to three times the normal capacity of a similar mundane container and ignores weight restrictions for non-magical items.</p><p><strong>It cannot store:</strong></p><ul><li>Living creatures</li><li>Active magical effects</li></ul><p>Once activated, the fetish functions as the expanded container until dismissed or long rest (ST discretion).</p><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 1. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 3. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=magpies-swag; rating=1; minGnosis=3; activation=action</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p>Fetish (Rating 1). Min Max Gnosis 3. Activate: action — Force (Wisdom/Gnosis check DC 11) or Appease (spend 1 Gnosis). Container holds 3× capacity, ignores weight for non-magical items; cannot store living creatures or active magical effects.</p>"
    },
